Aku akan ke sana. Jika melihat Seung Joo,

64
00:04:27,899 --> 00:04:29,769
suruh dia menunggu di sana.

65
00:04:30,670 --> 00:04:32,310
Pak Cho?

66
00:04:33,639 --> 00:04:34,779
Sudah ditutup. Astaga.

67
00:04:38,550 --> 00:04:40,350
Pukul berapa ini?

68
00:04:40,350 --> 00:04:42,290
Kenapa Seung Joo tidak datang?

69
00:04:42,350 --> 00:04:44,949
Tidak biasanya dia begini. Apa ada masalah?

70
00:04:44,949 --> 00:04:46,860
Maaf.

71
00:04:48,519 --> 00:04:51,490
Dia dalam perjalanan. Mohon tunggu sebentar.

72
00:04:51,490 --> 00:04:53,629
Tolong mengertilah.

73
00:04:55,129 --> 00:04:56,370
Ada apa?

74
00:04:57,470 --> 00:04:59,670
Ini masalah pribadi.

75
00:04:59,699 --> 00:05:01,839
- Pantas dia tidak di sini.
- Apa?

76
00:05:01,899 --> 00:05:03,639
Seung Joo pergi bersama Hyuk.

77
00:05:03,639 --> 00:05:05,279
Seharusnya mereka sudah di sini.

78
00:05:05,839 --> 00:05:07,410
Hyuk ke sana

79
00:05:07,410 --> 00:05:09,449
karena terjadi sesuatu kepada Seung Joo. Benar?

80
00:05:09,550 --> 00:05:11,410
Itu...

81
00:05:11,410 --> 00:05:13,720
Bukankah mereka kemari bersama?

82
