00:57:34,219 --> 00:57:35,329
Astaga.

948
00:57:35,329 --> 00:57:37,530
Kukira sepekan cukup.

949
00:57:37,530 --> 00:57:40,159
Aku sudah terlalu lama di rumah sakit.

950
00:57:40,159 --> 00:57:41,860
Aku sedang terburu-buru.

951
00:57:41,860 --> 00:57:43,829
Kamu tampak bahagia.

952
00:57:43,829 --> 00:57:45,199
Apa yang perlu dikhawatirkan?

953
00:57:45,199 --> 00:57:48,269
Kedatangan keluarga baru itu urusan penting.

954
00:57:48,400 --> 00:57:51,409
Dia hanya anak kecil. Tidak akan merepotkan.

955
00:57:51,409 --> 00:57:53,440
Kita harus memikirkan menu makanan.

956
00:57:53,440 --> 00:57:55,650
Kita hanya punya sayuran di rumah.

957
00:57:55,650 --> 00:57:58,679
Kita bisa ketinggalan bus.

958
00:57:58,679 --> 00:58:00,320
Cegatlah taksi.

959
00:58:02,420 --> 00:58:03,550
Taksi!

960
00:58:04,150 --> 00:58:06,219
Dia lebih hebat daripada kita.

961
00:58:06,219 --> 00:58:07,960
Dia sungguh cerdas.

962
00:58:07,960 --> 00:58:09,889
Taksinya di sini.

963
00:58:09,889 --> 00:58:11,230
Jangan lari.

964
00:58:11,230 --> 00:58:14,099
- Astaga.
- Ayo masuk.

965
00:58:17,400 --> 00:58:19,400
Ke mana dia?

966
00:58:22,409 --> 00:58:23,409
Kamu di sini?

967
00:58:26,280 --> 00:58:29,050
Aku sudah mencarinya di mana-mana.

968
00:58:29,349 --> 00:58:31,880
Mereka ke mana?

969
00:58:31,880 --> 00:58:33,679
Astaga!

970
00:58:34,320 --> 00:58:37,190
Ini parah. Parah!

971
00:58:40,690 --> 00:58:43,989
Bagaimana jika Pak Hong marah dan mengacau?

972
00:58:47,860 --> 00:58:48,969
"Oh Hyuk"

973
00:58:49,929 --> 00:58:51,429
Kamu di mana?

974
00:58:52,070 --> 00:58:53,340
Apa?

975
00:58:54,139 --> 00:58:56,309
Kalian pergi diam-diam tadi malam atau apa?

976
00:58:59,539 --> 00:59:01,409
Kami sedang menuju kampung halamanku.

977
00:59:01,480 --> 00:59:03,210
Kamu belum menuntaskan masalahnya,

978
00:59:03,210 --> 00:59:05,280
tapi malah pergi ke kampung halamanmu?

